    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "TO: THE DIRECTOR",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "DATE: October 9, 1950",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "FROM: MR. D. M. LADD",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING SAUCERS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "GREEN FIREBALLS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "PURPOSE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "To advise you of the most recent information known to the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Bureau concerning the captioned aerial phenomena.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "BACKGROUND",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "You will recall that on August 23, 1950, I furnished to you a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "memorandum regarding Project Twinkle set up by the Department of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Air Force, with the assistance of Land-Air, Inc., at Vaughn, New Mexico,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "for the purpose of obtaining data regarding these unusual aerial phenomena",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "which had been seen in the vicinity of sensitive installations in New",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Mexico. To date the Air Force has not advised us of any new developments",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "in connection with this project.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "[REDACTED] has",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "been contacted by the Albuquerque Office and arrangements have been made in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "order that the Bureau will be advised in the event any information relative",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "to these phenomena indicates any jurisdiction on the part of the Bureau.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "According to Bureau files, an average of approximately three or",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "four complaints have been received per month from June through September.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "These complaints were brought to the attention of OSI. A review of Bureau files",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "does not indicate that there has been any increase in the sightings of these",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "phenomena during or as a result of the war in Korea.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "JURISDICTION FOR INVESTIGATION OF THESE PHENOMENA",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "You will recall the investigation to obtain information concerning",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "these aerial phenomena is the jurisdiction of the Department of the Air Force.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "The Department of the Air Force is aware of our jurisdiction in matters",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "relating to espionage, sabotage and internal security, and we have contacted",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "OSI and requested them to advise us of any developments in connection with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "these phenomena which would be of interest to us as a result of our",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "jurisdiction.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "[unclear]",
      "status": "needs_image_check"
    },
    {
